---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Architecture — Nous Ergon" description="System architecture: six modules, three Step Function pipelines, autonomous parameter feedback.">
  <section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 pt-16 pb-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-zinc-100 mb-2">Architecture</h1>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      Six modules, three Step Function pipelines, autonomous parameter
      feedback. For the same map rendered statically with diagrams, see the
      <a class="text-sky-400 hover:text-sky-300 transition" href="https://github.com/cipher813/alpha-engine-docs">GitHub system README</a>.
      For per-module deep dives, see the per-repo READMEs.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-400 mb-3">The six modules</h2>
    <ul class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-8 list-disc list-inside">
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">Data</strong> &mdash; prices, macro, RAG corpus, universe features</li>
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">Research</strong> &mdash; 6 sector teams + CIO + macro economist, LLM-as-judge</li>
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">Predictor</strong> &mdash; L1 momentum/volatility GBMs + research calibrator &rarr; L2 Ridge meta-learner</li>
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">Executor</strong> &mdash; risk-gated sizing + intraday daemon</li>
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">Backtester</strong> &mdash; eval + parity + 4 config optimizers</li>
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">Dashboard</strong> &mdash; this site + the live console at live.nousergon.ai</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-400 mb-3">The three pipelines</h2>
    <ul class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed space-y-2 mb-8 list-disc list-inside">
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">Saturday</strong> &mdash; weekly research, predictor retrain, backtester evaluation + parameter optimization</li>
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">Weekday morning</strong> &mdash; predictor inference, executor planner, intraday daemon start</li>
      <li><strong class="text-zinc-100">EOD</strong> &mdash; post-market reconciliation, triggered by daemon shutdown after the trading day closes</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-sky-400 mb-3">Autonomous feedback loop</h2>
    <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">
      The backtester evaluates the system's own outputs each week, runs parameter
      sweeps, validates on holdout, and writes four optimized configs back to S3
      &mdash; Research / Predictor / Executor read on cold-start. The mechanism that
      makes Phase 3 alpha tuning a configuration flip rather than a code change.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
